Package Model

Class TaxiTrip

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.TaxiTrip
  • public class TaxiTrip
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the necessary data of a taxi trip/ cab trip. Takes care of declaring, initializing, saving its values and being able to obtain them or setting all its TaxiTrip attributes.

        This method constructor is used for initialize the attributes in base the arguments received. the passenger, address and destiny attributes are initialized based on the arguments received in the parameters.
        Parameters:
        passenger - the number of passengers
        address - the first client localization.
        destiny - the ultimate client localization.
        cost - the cost of the trip.
